  &lt;div class=&#34;photo&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4845911744?tag=baldandersinf-22&amp;amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;amp;th=1&amp;amp;psc=1&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51pDWTdSdlL._SL160_.jpg&#34; width=&#34;115&#34; alt=&#34;photo&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
